<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='433560' id='t-433560'>have a right to safe mobility,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='435627' id='t-435627'>without the risk of getting killed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='437900' id='t-437900'>And just as busways are,</span>
