<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497765' id='t-497765'>And I believe that our cities today</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='501122' id='t-501122'>have severe flaws,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='503237' id='t-503237'>and that different, better ones could be built.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='506795' id='t-506795'>What is wrong with our cities today?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509243' id='t-509243'>Well, for example, if we tell any three-year-old child</span>
