<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='581929' id='t-581929'>cities which show great respect</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='584684' id='t-584684'>for those most vulnerable citizens,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='586845' id='t-586845'>such as children or the elderly.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='588629' id='t-588629'>I will propose to you a couple of ingredients</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592434' id='t-592434'>which I think would make cities much better,</span>
