</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810740' id='t-810740'>The cities we are going to build</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='812255' id='t-812255'>over the next 50 years</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814095' id='t-814095'>will determine quality of life and even happiness</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='816492' id='t-816492'>for billions of people towards the future.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='818646' id='t-818646'>What a fantastic opportunity for leaders</span>
