<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='824466' id='t-824466'>especially in the developing countries.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='826533' id='t-826533'>They can create a much happier life</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='828380' id='t-828380'>for billions towards the future.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='829949' id='t-829949'>I am sure, I am optimistic,</span>
